Add Primary Image

 

To add additional primary image use "Add Primary Image" action. There is difference between a thumbnail of object and primary image. For example a sculpture could have more than one primary image, but only one image is presented as a thumbnail. 

    In the dialog:

    1. Enter search criteria to find the image you want to add as primary image and select search
    2. Select image(s) from the search result
    3. Press the Ok button
